Description: VibeOS desktop branding and four themes
 Ships four VibeOS KDE Look-and-Feel packages (Pacific Dawn, Outrun,
 Miami, Neon Grid) with matching color schemes, wallpaper packs
 (three time-of-day variants per theme), Plymouth boot splashes,
 Konsole color schemes, SDDM theming config, Orbitron + JetBrains
 Mono fonts, and the /etc/os-release branding.
 .
 After install the Pacific Dawn Look-and-Feel theme is applied
 system-wide as the default, and Plymouth is switched to the
 vibeos-pacific-dawn boot splash. Users can switch to any of the
 other three themes via Settings → Global Theme, or by asking
 Vibbey (e.g. "switch to outrun mode").
